<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>UTME Master Dashboard Test</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .feature {
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            border-left: 5px solid #667eea;
        }
        .feature h3 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
        .feature ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .feature li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            color: #555;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 25px;
        }
        .feature li:before {
            content: "✅";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
        }
        .tech-stack {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffecd2 0%, #fcb69f 100%);
            border-left-color: #ff6b6b;
        }
        .backend {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a8edea 0%, #fed6e3 100%);
            border-left-color: #4ecdc4;
        }
        .status {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d299c2 0%, #fef9d7 100%);
            border-radius: 15px;
        }
        .status h2 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .status-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .status-item {
            padding: 15px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .status-item.complete {
            border-left: 4px solid #4caf50;
        }
        .status-item.in-progress {
            border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1 class="title">🎯 UTME Master Dashboard</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Comprehensive Student Performance Analytics System</p>
        </div>

        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>📊 Dashboard Features</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Welcome header with motivational quotes</li>
                    <li>Quick stats cards (tests, scores, study hours)</li>
                    <li>Subject performance bar chart</li>
                    <li>Progress over time line chart</li>
                    <li>Recent activity timeline</li>
                    <li>Strengths & weaknesses analysis</li>
                    <li>Study recommendations</li>
                    <li>Premium upgrade prompts</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="feature tech-stack">
                <h3>🛠️ Frontend Tech Stack</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>React 18 with TypeScript</li>
                    <li>Recharts for data visualization</li>
                    <li>Framer Motion for animations</li>
                    <li>Zustand for state management</li>
                    <li>Tailwind CSS for styling</li>
                    <li>React Hot Toast for notifications</li>
                    <li>Lucide React for icons</li>
                    <li>Zod for form validation</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="feature backend">
                <h3>⚙️ Backend Implementation</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Express.js with TypeScript</li>
                    <li>Prisma ORM with PostgreSQL</li>
                    <li>JWT authentication</li>
                    <li>Dashboard analytics controller</li>
                    <li>Subject performance calculations</li>
                    <li>Progress tracking algorithms</li>
                    <li>Study recommendations engine</li>
                    <li>Premium feature access control</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="status">
            <h2>🚀 Implementation Status</h2>
            <div class="status-grid">
                <div class="status-item complete">
                    <h4>✅ Dashboard Components</h4>
                    <p>All UI components created with modern design</p>
                </div>
                <div class="status-item complete">
                    <h4>✅ Charts & Analytics</h4>
                    <p>Recharts integration with interactive visualizations</p>
                </div>
                <div class="status-item complete">
                    <h4>✅ Backend API</h4>
                    <p>Complete dashboard controller with analytics</p>
                </div>
                <div class="status-item complete">
                    <h4>✅ Type Safety</h4>
                    <p>Full TypeScript coverage with proper types</p>
                </div>
                <div class="status-item complete">
                    <h4>✅ State Management</h4>
                    <p>Zustand store for dashboard data</p>
                </div>
                <div class="status-item complete">
                    <h4>✅ Responsive Design</h4>
                    <p>Mobile-friendly with Tailwind CSS</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; color: #666;">
            <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong> Test the dashboard, integrate with real exam data, and deploy for production use.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                🎓 Ready to revolutionize UTME preparation with data-driven insights!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>